event_highlights_audio::clip_card_4::goa: Nama baayyee namatti tolu ta'ee taatecharratti hirmaate waraabi.
event_highlights_audio::clip_card_1::goa: Namoota taatecharratti hirmaataa jiran yookaan deebii gochaa waan ta'aa jirurratti kennan waraabi. Sochiin qaamakeetii jiraachuun gaarii godha.
event_highlights_audio::clip_card_3::goa: Namoota baayyee namatti talani fi  taatecharratti  hirmaatan waraabi.
event_highlights_audio::title: Agarsiistuu Taatee
event_highlights_audio::clip_card_7::goa: Dubbii ijoo yookaan xumura ajaa'ibaa barbaadi waraabi. Xumura taphaa yookaan gocha yookaan haasawaa iyyuu, fakkeenyyaf.
event_highlights_audio::clip_card_5::goa: Kutaa taatechaa baayyee adda ta'e waraabi.
event_highlights_audio::clip_card_6::goa: Taatecharratti namoota barbaachisoo ta'an waraabi. Fakkeenyaaf, dubbataa yookaan geggeessaa ijoo taatechaa yookaan namoota kabajamoo, namoota siyaasaa, namoota bebbeekamoo hirmaatan.
